headline: Is DuPont de Nemours (DD) Fairly Priced After 36% One Year Share Price Gain?
summary: If you are wondering whether DuPont de Nemours at US$43.38 is giving you fair value for your money, you are not alone. This article is designed to help you size that up clearly. The stock has posted returns of 1.1% over the last 7 days, 4.6% over 30 days, 6.1% year to date and 36.5% over the past year, with a 49.9% return over 3 years and 46.6% over 5 years.
